descriptionHtml:
---- CBBE Tsun Female Armor Version 1.1 ----


----Updates----
Version 1.1: Added missing Textures & Fix Shoes clipping

----Description----
This armor is a female version of Tsun\'s Armor (Tsun is the guy in sovngarde). There are couple of clipping issues but nothing to that should to major.

- I tried to get most of the clipping but I\'m pretty sure I missed some.

Obtaining:
-Craft at Forge (Under Steel)


----Manual Installation----
Installing:copy the Data folder inside the zip and merge it with your own Data folder (and merge them together).

Uninstall: Delete installed files.

Files Installed:
.../Data/meshes/FJ_Gear/tsunarmor/tsun0.nif
.../Data/meshes/FJ_Gear/tsunarmor/tsun1.nif
.../Data/meshes/FJ_Gear/tsunarmor/tsunboots_0.nif
.../Data/meshes/FJ_Gear/tsunarmor/tsunboots_1.nif
../Data/textures/FJ_Gear/Tsun/Steelarmor.dds
../Data/textures/FJ_Gear/Tsun/Steelarmor_n.dds
../Data/textures/FJ_Gear/Tsun/Steelarmor_m.dds
Note: the textures  for tsun are from the original textures.


----Credits----
-Bethesda\'s Meshes & Textures
-Caliente\'s CBBE Body

----FAQ---

Q: I don\'t like X or Y can you change that? 
A: If it\'s not a a bug or glitch then sorry buddy your gonna have change that yourself. I\'m heading on to the next mod on my list.

Q:Can you convert this another body type?
A: No, if you want another body type version, you can make it. I\'d rather make more mods than spend time converting to other body types.
author: Fallen Judge
